name: Chewy Token
description: Chewy Token is a IP focused meme coin on Aptos Network. With Art, Memes & Short videos, Chewy Token celebrates the people who kept chewing and embraced the spirit of resilience the crypto community, with relatable memes. Chewy Token has also collaborated with several Solana Artists to fuse Art with Memes all while introducing several artists to the Aptos Ecosystem. Besides being a meme coin Chewy Token doesnot have much utility.
